Description
  A bash script for Ubuntu to install TeamSpeak3 Server.

Usage
  Firewall ports
    Minimum
      - 9987/udp: used for Voice.
      - 30033/tcp: used for File Transfer.

    Optional
      - 10011/tcp: used for ServerQuery raw (Recommended).
      - 10022/tcp: used for ServerQuery SSH.
      - 10080/tcp: used for WebQuery HTTP.
      - 10443/tcp: used for WebQuery HTTPS.
      - 41144/tcp: used for DNS.
